expression.expression-string: AggregateIterable<ProgramSubscription> prgsub = database.getCollection("Users", ProgramSubscription.class).aggregate(Arrays.asList( match(eq("_id", userid)), unwind("$programSubscriptions"), project( fields(excludeId(), include("programSubscriptions"))), match(eq("programSubscriptions.idprogram", programid)), replaceRoot("$programSubscriptions") )).iterator().next();
